                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">Climate Dynamics & Forecasting in the USA</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">My research investigates long-term climatic shifts and develops advanced forecasting models to support water management and climate adaptation in the United States, with a special focus on Texas. By analyzing decades of data and applying machine learning, I aim to provide actionable intelligence for navigating climate uncertainty.</p>
                
